”Alexa, open party bash night”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: party bash night
des: This entertaining multiplayer party game involves two to six teams. They have to guess their knowledge on the selected participant. The special person (the selected person who judges the answers) will judge players on how well they know him/her. Alexa judges the responses. Please note: This skill was created using the Bachelorette Game Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
